      "side": 1,
      "message": "The buildbucket output would need to be modified to produce a multiline string for the properties. Right now it\u0027s just a single line json blob. Where would I make that change?\n\nWith a generator that turns it into a multiline string, running lucicfg compiled with this change breaks it up into multiple strings as expected.",
