      "writtenOn": "2021-06-24T22:33:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It looks good, except that each of the strings ends with \\n, which might be a little confusing. I also worry that if a property had a \\n in its value (say a regex), then it would result in really odd formatting. So I\u0027m wondering if instead of making this general for all string fields if ToTextPB should just have handling specific to the buildbucket properties or if proto fields could be annotated in some way to indicate it should be formatted as multiple lines.",
      "parentUuid": "9a73444a_d2739b4d",
      "revId": "8a2b567d9aaf6a29dddbae3c752fc6adb74aef10",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
